com.sun.mdm.index.master.search.transaction
Class TransactionSummary

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.mdm.index.master.search.transaction.TransactionSummary
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TransactionSummary
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The TransactionSummary class represents an object containing a transaction summary returned by a call to lookupTransaction. A transaction history search returns an iterator of TransactionSummary objects.
